Background

		Mr. Yakov Faitelson, also known as Yaki, Co-founded Varonis Systems, Inc. in 2004 and has been its Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President since 2004. Mr. Faitelson is responsible for leading the management, strategic direction and execution of Varonis Vision. He held key leadership positions in the global professional services, product development and systems integration divisions of NetVision and Network Appliance.	
	



